data.description: First time home buyers, check out this lovely 2 bedroom 1 bath home with 1,198 sq ft of living space on a 6,689 sq ft lot in a very residential neighborhood, laminate flooring, double sided windows for sound, upgraded plumbing and electrical throughout the home, separate dining room for family dinners, 2 large size bedrooms, inside laundry room, large living room with fireplace and recently upgraded bathroom. long driveway with plenty of parking space leading up to a 2 car garage in the large private back yard with plenty of potential to create your own entertaining backyard setting, add an ADU or maybe even your own pool. This home is centrally located and 10 minutes to SoFi Stadium and newly being built Intuit Dome also 30 minutes from LAX, local beaches and near most fwys close to plenty of big supermarket shopping and walking distance to local schools.
